Class FSM

  • java.lang.Object
    • FSM
  • public class FSM
extends Object
    A string-to-token parser class that employs the methodology of a finite state machine The class takes no parameters upon instantiation, but its primary method, parsePoly(), takes in a string and a memory to convert the string into a list of Tokens, and to access the stored objects from the Polynomial class.
